Morphology of 
<taxonomicName id="23B468D5FFA2FF96FE23FA04FDF6FA1E" authority="Andrade-Sorcia &amp; Riosmena-Rodríguez &amp; Muñiz-Salazar &amp; López-Vivas &amp; Boo &amp; Lee &amp; Boo, 2014" authorityName="Andrade-Sorcia &amp; Riosmena-Rodríguez &amp; Muñiz-Salazar &amp; López-Vivas &amp; Boo &amp; Lee &amp; Boo" authorityYear="2014" box="[416,581,1511,1532]" class="Phaeophyceae" family="Sargassaceae" genus="Sargassum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Fucales" pageId="12" pageNumber="213" phylum="Ochrophyta" rank="species" species="ulixei" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="D6C0CF44FFA2FF96FE23FA04FDF6FA1E" box="[416,581,1511,1532]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="213">Sargassum ulixei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="CDF3723FFFA2FF96FDCEFA04FD2AFA1E" box="[589,665,1511,1532]" pageId="12" pageNumber="213" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
A. Habit. B, C. Section of axial cells (a) and medullar cells (m). D. Holdfast. E. Sessile blades (arrow head), vesicles (arrow), and receptacles growing above the branch. F–H. Receptacles, zygote (z).
